title: TechArts 3D Custom Girl Creator XPr1
description:
This is the TechArts 3D Custom Girl creator with XPr1. 

This one is UNCENSORED!!!

Note that the configuration utility does not completely work with either of these. When you change your settings you must hit Start for them to be applied. However, the utility will crash and not launch the game. You must use the normal shortcut.

Sorry, I can't fix this, as I didn't code the utility. Just be sure to hit Start to apply your changes!
